folder struct
(1)do.py is responsible for get common  environment and configure environment in
user mode
(2)sudo_env.py is responsible for some special configure environment and reset
configure for example nfs,tftp in root mode.
(3)sudo.py is responsible for auto install software in root mode
(4)sudo_driver.py is responsible for auto insatll necessary device driver in
root mode

